  "texts": [
    "Specifically, the (CNN) model achieved an accuracy of 89.87%, while (CNN-LSTM) scored 88.61%.",
    "Notably, the (CNN) model also boasted significantly faster training times, approximately 2.8 times faster than CNN-LSTM.",
    "In contrast, the Bi-LSTM model scored an average accuracy of 61.52%, while the (LSTM) model struggled with just 55.06%.",
    "Table 8 lists the median results across all metrics during the five folds.",
    "It is essential to emphasize that while the results may not be outstanding, this represents an initial experiment."
